<?xml version="1.0" encoding="GB2312"?>
<Body>
	<Title>广东发生食物中毒事件 牛肉丸毒倒200多小学生</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2004年9月10日</ReportTime>
	<Content>
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e1"><Time tid="t1" type="relTime">昨天下午</Time>，<Location lid="l1">佛山市南海区里水镇旗峰中学</Location>发生特大群体<Denoter did="d1" type="emergency">食物中毒</Denoter>事件</Event>，<Event eid="e2">该中学内的小学四、五、六年级<Participant sid="s2">500多名学生</Participant><Denoter did="d2" type="action">吃</Denoter>完<Object oid="o2">午餐</Object>后</Event>，<Event eid="e3"><Time tid="t3" type="relTime">下午3时左右</Time>陆续<Denoter did="d3" type="stateChange">发生</Denoter><Participant sid="s3">大批学生</Participant>肚疼、腹泻、呕吐等<Object oid="o3">现象</Object></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e4">根据<Participant sid="s4">记者</Participant><Denoter did="d4" type="operation">调查</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e5">有<Participant sid="s5">200多名小学生</Participant>分别被<Denoter did="d5" type="movement">送往</Denoter><Location lid="l5">里水医院</Location>、<Location lid="l5">沙涌门诊部</Location>、<Location lid="l5">大沥</Location>、<Location lid="l5">黄岐</Location>等镇级医院</Event><Event eid="e6"><Denoter did="d6" type="operation">抢救</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e7"><Object oid="o7">旗峰中学</Object>已被<Participant sid="s7">警察</Participant><Denoter did="d7" type="operation">封锁</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e8"><Participant sid="s8">南海区及里水镇的各级领导</Participant><Denoter did="d8" type="movement">赴</Denoter><Location lid="l8" type="destination">各个医院</Location></Event><Event eid="e9">进行<Denoter did="d9" type="operation">指挥抢救</Denoter></Event>和<Event eid="e10"><Denoter did="d10" type="operation">布置工作</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e11"><Participant sid="s11">当地卫生防疫</Participant>、<Participant sid="s11">监测</Participant>等部门正在<Denoter did="d11" type="operation">查找</Denoter><Object oid="o11">原因</Object></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence>截止<Event eid="e12"><Time tid="t12" type="relTime">昨晚</Time><Participant sid="s12">记者</Participant><Denoter did="d12" type="action">发稿</Denoter></Event>时，<Event eid="e13"><Participant sid="s12">南海区委</Participant>、<Participant sid="s12">区政府</Participant><Denoter did="d12" type="operation">召开</Denoter><Object oid="o12">新闻发布会</Object></Event>，介绍是发生一起43名小学生细菌性急性胃肠炎事件，并无危重病人。</Sentence></Paragraph>
	</Content>
	<eRelation relType="Causal" cause_eid="e2" effect_eid="e3"/>
	
	
</Body>